NAME:

    phpGACL - PHP based Access Control Lists.

VERSION: v0.9beta

AUTHORS:
    
    Mike Benoit <ipso@snappymail.ca>

MAILING LISTS:

    See here: http://sourceforge.net/mail/?group_id=57103

INSTALL:
	
	Edit config.inc.php to setup database connection parameters
	Run setup.php in your web browsers to initialize database

SYNOPSIS:

    require("gacl.inc.php");

    if ( acl_check( <Access Control Object> , <Access Request Object> ) ) {
		echo "Access Granted!";
    } else {
		echo "Access Denied!";
    }


DESCRIPTION:

    See here: http://phpgacl.sourceforge.net/

